### ============================================================
### 경험치 시스템 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 경험치 정보 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/experience/me
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 경험치 획득 이력 조회 (페이징)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/experience/me/history?page=0&size=20
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 레벨별 필요 경험치 설정 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/experience/levels
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 레벨 설정 생성/수정 (Admin용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/experience/levels?level=1&requiredExp=0&cumulativeExp=0&title=Beginner&description=Welcome to the journey
Accept: application/json
